{"tid":2086593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"孟加拉裔青年認18區「開花」刑事損壞交通燈 即時還柙候判 須賠逾萬元","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T11:11:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"49233ca423a3e35f2c8de64bcea16652ca39fdb8","tid":2086593,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075026&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2FyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=ac9703b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075026&h=e3800a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075026</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）去年10月13日網民發起18區「開花」，全港多處有人破壞港鐵車站設施及交通設備以癱瘓交通。17歲孟加拉裔青年涉破壞交通燈，今日（30日）在九龍城裁判法院承認一項刑事損壞罪，須還柙至7月14日判刑，期間等待更新中心、社會服務令及勞教中心報告。被告另須向機電工程署賠償10,409元。"},{"pid":"b1bdb6ee1940d66046746bcb3b55ca5ae7ef5ef2","tid":2086593,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f892fb1eb21295bbfbd29629513f059b6db437d3","tid":2086593,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda13b83b299db2ff7fb3b1c6ed76a8e3b33e17d","tid":2086593,"uid":201359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"另須向機電工程署賠償10,409元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/